    </div>
</div>

<p><img src="/images/malta/marriott/marriott-23.jpg." alt="marriott-23.jpg" /></p>

<p>It was hard to leave all the loveliness and luxury and go to bed, but it was definitely worth it for the rooms. We all know how important a comfortable bed and beautiful linen is for a proper night’s sleep. The Malta Marriott has elevated sleeping well into an art form.</p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/marriott/marriott-37.jpg." alt="marriott-37.jpg" /></p>

