    </div>
</div>

<p>Dinner is out of this world in Taro at the Villa and they can offer a sommelier to help you pair your wines with your food for a truly exclusive evening.</p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/marriott/marriott-18.jpg." alt="marriott-18.jpg" /></p>

