<p>As always, my love for good food and incredibly good wine has to be balanced with my need to fit into my clothes!</p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/marriott/marriott-2.jpg." alt="marriott-2.jpg" /></p>

<p>The Malta Marriott not only has a ‘fitness center’ which offers free classes to guests, but also the beautiful Myoka Spa, a gorgeous indoor pool and a very glamourous pool deck and rooftop pool. So no excuses but, equally, you will feel no guilt at loving all the pampering and indulgence.</p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/marriott/marriott-42.jpg." alt="marriott-42.jpg" /></p>

